		<li><b>Contact</b>: This lists your email address and other the various ways you would like people to get in touch with you.<span class="inside-ol">&nbsp;</span>Amend these contact details to your own. You can add or remove different social media contact points, such as Twitter, Facebook, YouTube or Instagram, as required.<span class="inside-ol">&nbsp;</span>
